<div class="description">
    <h3>Description</h3>

    <div class="body">
        <p>It is currently not possible to retrieve a Zend_Db_Table_Rowset from Zend_Paginator. This is due to the fact that it's not possible to get the table instance from a Zend_Db_Table_Select query.
A workaround for this problem could be an additional setTable() method in the DbSelect adapter. If a table is provided using this method, the DbSelect adapter will return a Rowset.</p>

